## Quick Recap (I'm Open To Suggestions For This One)

- 80% of your UI is gray. Make it a good gray.
- Pick one primary color. Use it at multiple shades.
- Use semantic colors for status. Don't invent new meanings.
- Too many colors equals chaos. Less is more and more professional.
